    <title><anchor id="Anchor595506" role="Index"
    xreflabel="items:by class code;class codes:item details for" /> <indexterm
        significance="normal" zone="Anchor595506">
        <primary>items</primary>

        <secondary>by class code</secondary>
      </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal" zone="Anchor595506">
        <primary>class codes</primary>

        <secondary>item details for</secondary>
      </indexterm>Items by Class Code</title>

    <para id="Para520262">To view Items by Class Code, select the "Items by
    Class Code" option. The following screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para520266"><screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="images/PD_Disp_itemsClassCode.png"
                       id="Graphic563623" />
          </imageobject>

          <caption id="Caption520267">Items by Class Code</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot></para>

    <para id="Para520268">When displaying Items by Class Code, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para617038">All Class Codes</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923d38">
          <para>Select to display Items for all Class Codes.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520269">Selected</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923d80">
          <para>Specify Class Code whose Items you want to display.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para593272">Pattern</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923dc8">
          <para>Enter a Class Code pattern to select a range of Class
          Codes.</para>

          <para id="Para664823">Refine your search using Regular Expressions,
          as described in <link endterm="Anchor77806" id="XRef664822"
          linkend="Anchor77806"> Pattern Matching with Regular
          Expressions</link>"Topic: Pattern Matching with Regular
          Expressions".</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520273">Show Inactive Items</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192ba00">
          <para>Select to show Inactive Items in the display.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520274">Items</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192ba48">
          <para>Display lists Items by Class Code, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para520276">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para618188">CLOSE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bab4">
          <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para618197">QUERY</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bafc">
          <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para663984">PRINT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bb44">
          <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para556970">Right-clicking on an Item in the Items list enables
    you to select from the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520285">Edit Item Master</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bbb0">
          <para></para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <xi:include href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml"
